=== 积分系统 ===
假使积分排名出现同分状况时，将比较车手获得的分站冠军数，决定最终的排行榜名次。排名前十名的車手能夠獲得積分，而刷出最快圈速的車手必須在前十名才能獲得1分最快圈速積分。<ref name="points regs">{{Cite web|url=https://www.fia.com/file/78014/download/26183|title=2019 Formula One Sporting Regulations|date=2019-03-12|website=[[Fédération_Internationale_de_l'Automobile|fia]].com|pages=3–4, 41|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190313225312/https://www.fia.com/file/78014/download/26183|archive-date=2019-03-13|access-date=2019-11-27}}</ref> 衝刺賽將在賽程上其中三場比賽進行衝刺賽，車手將在周六進行100公里的比賽。衝刺賽的前八名車手將能夠獲得積分。<ref name="Sprint Race">{{cite web|url=https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article.formula-1-to-hold-three-sprint-events-in-2022-with-more-points-on-offer.4UXmrMDm6We04ZFlW0Ieo9.html|title=Formula 1 to hold three Sprint events in 2022 – with more points on offer|website=formula1.com|date=2022-02-15|access-date=2022-02-15|archive-date=2022-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220307204206/https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article.formula-1-to-hold-three-sprint-events-in-2022-with-more-points-on-offer.4UXmrMDm6We04ZFlW0Ieo9.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 夺冠车手必须完成75%的赛程，方能获得全额积分。若未完成指定赛程，积分根据状况分配之。

